<a href="/questions/128804-i-ve-read-a-lot-of-dr-dyer-s-previous">I&#39;ve read a lot of Dr Dyer&#39;s previous work. Can anyone comment on whether they believe this title has a fresh insight?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_128804'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F19793.The_Power_of_Intention">like</a></span>

