<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link244793" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=244793&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F128804-i-ve-read-a-lot-of-dr-dyer-s-previous%2Fanswers%2F244793-your-perspective-of">flag</a>
</div>
