        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2000658" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14992771870789074368">Dr. Dyer sees intention as an inner awareness &quot;that exists in the universe as an invisible force of energy.&quot; In this book he links intention to the creative power of the universe and suggests that it is within each one of us, the power to change the world.</span>
  <span id="freeText14992771870789074368" style="display:none">Dr. Dyer sees intention as an inner awareness "that exists in the universe as an invisible force of energy." In this book he links intention to the creative power of the universe and suggests that it is within each one of us, the power to change the world.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14992771870789074368" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
